snippet.title: Godzilla The Arcade Game (Playthrough Pt. 1/11)
snippet.description:
Playthrough of the 1993 Godzilla Arcade Game, part one of eleven.

The first level has Godzilla fighting against his classic nemesis, King Ghidorah. Rodan can be seen making a cameo appearance flying by.
